STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Christopher David VOGEL, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0230 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 19, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

Christopher Vogel appeals his sentence following his guilty plea to animal abuse. SENTENCE VACATED IN PART AND REMANDED.

SENTENCE VACATED IN PART. REMANDED.
